SELECT * FROM emp001     where    deptno+20    BETWEEN   -1||0   AND     0   order by  empno;
SELECT * FROM emp001     where    deptno    LIKE  '%'||'2%'   order by  empno;   

--error  1064
SELECT * FROM emp002     where    deptno-20    BETWEEN   -1||0   AND      0   order by  empno;
SELECT * FROM emp002     where    deptno    LIKE  '%'||'2%'   order by  empno;  



